getResponse

java.lang.Object getResponse()
The answer to the question posed by this AlertParameter. This method would be used by the UI to fill in the user's response, if any.

isVisible

boolean isVisible()
Should this parameter be visible. Invisible parameters simply carry information needed to handle the alert when it is acknowledged.

isEditable

boolean isEditable()
Should this parameter be editable. Uneditable parameters simply supply additional information to the operator, but the operator can't change them.
